title: Dyno Run: Honda Accord (2008-09) with the Takeda Short Ram Air Intake System
description: This 2.4-liter Honda Accord gains an additional +13 hp and +16 ft/lbs of torque when it hits the dyno with Takeda Short Ram Air Intake System.
tags: Takeda Short Ram Air Intake System, Short Ram Intake, Honda Accord Dyno

asset.title: Dyno Honda Accord (2008-09) with a Takeda Short Ram Air Intake System
asset.description:
This 2.4-liter Honda Accord hits the dyno with a cold air intake from Takeda, an AFE company. The Accord's only modification is the Takeda short ram intake and it lets the engine gain an additional +13 horsepower and +16 ft/lbs of torque!

Find out what a Takeda intake can do for your vehicle at AutoAnything: http://www.autoanything.com/air-intakes/20A53592A1.aspx

Or view all intake products here: http://www.autoanything.com/air-intakes/10A50208.aspx
